some other info:

RUN LEVELS: Default run level is 3
---------------------------------
to check: who -r 
to change the run level, ex: inti 1/2/3/...
----------------------------------------------

inti 0 -- shutdown
inti 1 -- single user mode
init 2 -- multi user mode 
init 3 -- multi user mode, all config
init 4 -- reserved
init 5 -- GUI
init 6 -- reboot/restart





